issue.title: Use leaflet.js to paint geojson
issue.body:
Please use https://github.com/toladata/GLADMap/blob/master/data/AFG/afg_2.json as sample

There will be multiple geojson files, please ensure you have a function in which we can add path to multiple geojson files.

issue.title: Create a script/command which takes multiple geodatabase and generate similar geojson file
issue.body:
Example path - http://biogeo.ucdavis.edu/data/gadm2.8/shp/AFG_adm_shp.zip

We might be able to replace country code and get new file. All download files must be present in "./tmp"
1. goto ./tmp and unzip all files
2. cd directory and fetch "{country_code_adm3.shp}"
3. convert using ogr2ogr to same name geojson. Place geojson in ./data/{country_code}/{file_name}
